subject: An email was sent to you somet
body:
An email was sent to you sometime last week with the expectation of
receiving a return email from you, but to my surprise, you never
bothered to reply. Please reply for further explanation.

subject: Re: An email was sent to you somet
body:
Hello there,

Oh, I'm so sorry for the inconvenience. I must have missed your email last week. Could you please tell me more about what it was regarding? I'd be happy to help in any way that I can.

Looking forward to hearing from you soon!

Best wishes,
Peggy
